{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-02602/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-02602"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["0:26:02"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Creator"]},"value":{"none":["Paul Thomas Anderson"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["plan américain"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["A man tests a blue fabric against a model."]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-02602","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-02602"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1/27d5a07e-73f6-44ef-8b64-2bdb5b7fc31d","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:31:45.070Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds is wearing glasses here, as he continues to evaluate in more detail Alma’s suitability for the role of muse.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:1341.1574697173621,225.3835800807537,227.4024226110364,204.1453566621804"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1/f605b6bb-7d16-46a7-9e04-4eb2e0f85a25","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T14:32:44.952Z","creator":"g","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>The composition of this shot places Alma (on a pedestal) in a slightly higher plane than Reynolds, which foreshadows the shift in their relationship power dynamic towards the end of the film. Similarly, Reynolds stands under a spotlight between Alma and the edge of the frame, a sign of his position in the narrative: his relationship with Alma will bring to light something that was hidden, yet will somewhat trap him (or at least restrict his movement when he becomes ill).</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-02602/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:36.177658142664086,39.32705248990622,360.48452220726807,217.06594885598932"}}}]}]}]}